and he lets us go together to have fun.

112
00:08:27,908 --> 00:08:29,328
You can organize it.

113
00:08:30,149 --> 00:08:33,668
- Why you two don't do it?
- Let me help you.

114
00:08:34,828 --> 00:08:37,708
Let him help you. I might not go.

115
00:08:38,149 --> 00:08:41,269
