274
00:23:17,509 --> 00:23:20,029
- Ready to jump.
- One, two, three, go!

275
00:23:23,868 --> 00:23:25,388
- Let's go
- You first.

276
00:23:28,348 --> 00:23:29,229
So fun!

277
00:23:31,029 --> 00:23:33,669
