Where did she go?

278
00:23:34,068 --> 00:23:35,989
- I will go look for her.
- Wait.

279
00:23:36,029 --> 00:23:37,949
You go down first!

280
00:23:39,989 --> 00:23:40,868
Splash water on him.

281
00:23:47,108 --> 00:23:47,989
